title: Board Identification Suggestions
message: I'm working on a 2015 A1502 and I just received a shipment of donor boards for various macbooks. The A1502 logic board has 2 stickers, neither of which have the apple part number or the part number that sellers have listed. What numbers or letters on the stickers do you use to identify what board you're looking at?

title: Board Identification Suggestions
message: It's not a sticker it is in the solder mask.
